These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-1::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, tram, bike
1. the person driving the bike is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2   |   3    |
| Transport   | van | tram | bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, nurse, security-guard
1. the nurse is on the far left or far right##3
2. the security-guard is in the middle##1
3. the security-guard is on the right of the paramedic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2   |   3   |
| Job   | paramedic | security-guard | nurse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-3::.
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, mouse, lizard
1. the owner of the lizard is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Pet   | mouse | hedgehog | lizard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-4::.
City: san-francisco, berlin, nizza
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3    |
| City   | san-francisco | berlin | nizza |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-5::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, zinnia, dahlia
1. the person who growsdahlia is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |   3    |
| Flower   | balloon-flower | zinnia | dahlia |

