.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, adventure, romance
1. the person watching romance movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching drama movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | adventure | romance |

