.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-13::.
3 different pets are kept: frog, pony, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the owner of the pony and the owner of the frog##2
3. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3     |
| Pet   | pony | guinea-pig | frog |

